OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMorning fog and low cloud will
OL,6,Flift to give a dry and mild day, with
OL,7,Fbrighter spells. Cloud will thicken
OL,8,Ffrom the west in the afternoon, with
OL,9,Fpossible rain later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FOvercast with low cloud and
OL,12,Flight rain and drizzle at times
OL,13,Fovernight, hill fog likely over higher
OL,14,Fground. Winds gradually increasing by
OL,15,Fthe morning.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FCloudy to start, becoming
OL,18,Fovercast with rain and showers moving
OL,19,Fin from the west during the afternoon
OL,20,Fand overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
